               <msContents>
                  <summary> A complete copy of the <title>Muntakhab al-Lubāb</title> (Selections of
                     the Intellects) by Muḥammad Hāshim Khāfī Khān (ca. 1663–1731). Comprised of
                     three books, the first covers pre-Mughal dynasties up to the Lodi Sultanate.
                     The second relates the history of the Timurid dynasty and their Mughal
                     descendants up to the reign of Emperor Akbar, including the Sur interregnum;
                     The third volume covers the reigns of Jahangīr to the 14th year of the reign of
                        <persName role="subject" key="person_45680638"
                        ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/45680638">Muḥammad Shāh (b. 1702, r.
                        1719–1748)</persName>, in 1742. Since the events he records from 1669 to
                     1742 reflect his own experiences and events that he personally witness,
                     historians deem it an invaluable source on the later Mughal period.</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_822-item1">
                     <author key="person_44737861" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/44737861">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Khāfī Khān, Muḥammad
                           Hāshim, ca. 1663–1731</persName>; <lb/>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">خافی خان، محمد هاشم</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="main" key="work_551">Muntakhab
                        al-Lubāb</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" type="main" key="work_551">منتخب اللباب</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" key="work_551">Tarikh-i Khafi
                        Khan</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" type="alt" key="work_551">تاریخ خافی خان</title>

                     <incipit xml:lang="ar" type="basmalla"><locus type="page" from="1" to="1">
                           صقحه‌ی ۱ (page 1):</locus> جهان جهان شکره و سپاس افزودن از قیاس پادشاهی
                        را سزاست که بمقتضای حکمت بالغه وجود جهانداران... </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa"><locus type="page" from="806" to="806"> صقحه‌ی ۸۰۶
                           (page 806):</locus> ...بعد افغان کشی زیاد فوجها جایچا(؟) برای اخراخ(ج)
                        افغان و فوج روم یقین نمود بعد مدت است و نه سال سریر آرای ملک موروثی گردید </explicit>
                     <colophon><locus type="page" from="806" to="806"> صقحه‌ی ۸۰۶ (page
                           806):</locus> تمت الکتاب المسمی بمنتخب اللباب</colophon>
                     <colophon>Uninformative colophon.</colophon>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>

                  </msItem>
